{"route":{"route":"/posts/23567986/","outputPath":"posts/23567986/index.html","kind":"post","title":"golangとollamaでfunction calling","language":"ja","params":{"abbrlink":"23567986"}},"description":"今回はollamaのオフィシャルクライアントでfuncation callingを使いたいです。 前回はlangchaingoで使っただけと、試してたらollamaの引数toolsは無効です、githubの実例ollama functions exampleはsystem messageとtoolsのjsonを組み合わ","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/golangとollamaでfunction-calling.md","route":"/posts/23567986/","abbrlink":"23567986","title":"golangとollamaでfunction calling","date":"2024-11-11 19:11:06","updated":"2024-11-11 19:11:06","tags":["llm","function calling","text embedding"],"categories":["llm"],"language":"ja","htmlLang":"ja","locale":"ja_JP","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"ja-JP","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>今回はollamaのオフィシャルクライアントでfuncation callingを使いたいです。　　<br>\n前回はlangchaingoで使っただけと、試してたらollamaの引数toolsは無効です、githubの実例<a href=\"https://github.com/tmc/langchaingo/blob/main/examples/ollama-functions-example/ollama_functions_example.go\">ollama_functions_example</a>はsystem messageとtoolsのjsonを組み合わせて内容を生成する。例えば：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">systemMessage</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span></span> <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> bs, err := json.Marshal(functions)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  log.Fatal(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> fmt.Sprintf(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`You have access to the following tools:</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-string\"></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">%s</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-string\"></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">To use a tool, respond with a JSON object with the following structure: </span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">{</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-string\"> &quot;tool&quot;: &lt;name of the called tool&gt;,</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-string\"> &quot;tool_input&quot;: &lt;parameters for the tool matching the above JSON schema&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">}</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">`</span>, <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>(bs))</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>これはちょっと優雅でない、<code>ollama/api</code>を使いたいと思います。</p>\n<h2 id=\"function-callingとは\">function callingとは</h2>\n<p>llmのレスポンスが外部関数の呼び出しを検知し、関数の結果を組み合わせて内容を生成する機能です。　　<br>\n例えば：「東京の天気は？」はpromptをとして、「晴れです」と生成する。　　<br>\n大勢のllmはfunction callingをtoolと読んでいる、呼び出しどき引数として引き渡して内容を生成する。　　</p>\n<!-- \nprimjs can't support exclude languages,\nso we direct use hexo tag system\n -->\n<div class=\"mermaid mermaid-pending\" data-mermaid-source=\"sequenceDiagram\n    actor ユーザ\n    ユーザ-&gt;&gt;サーバー: 東京の天気は？\n    サーバー-&gt;&gt;llm: promptとtools\n    llm--)サーバー: 関数を呼び出し&lt;br/&gt;引数（東京）を返す\n    サーバー-&gt;&gt;外部サービス: 東京の天気を取得\n    外部サービス--)サーバー: 天気を返す\n    サーバー-&gt;&gt;llm: 天気をpromptに追加\n    llm--&gt;&gt;サーバー: 生成する内容を返す\n    サーバー-&gt;&gt;ユーザ: 内容を返す\n\" aria-busy=\"true\"></div><!-- \n取得：しゅとく\n -->\n<h2 id=\"goで実現\">goで実現</h2>\n<p>関数と引数の説明(Description)は自然な言葉で良いです、一般的なプログラミングとはちょっと違うと思います。</p>\n<p>toolsの定義</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;github.com/ollama/ollama/api&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">tools := api.Tool{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      Type: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;function&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      Function: api.ToolFunction{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">       Name:        <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;getCurrentWeather&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">       Description: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Get the current weather for a city&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">       Parameters: <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">struct</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        Type       <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>   <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;json:\\&quot;type\\&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        Required   []<span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;json:\\&quot;required\\&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        Properties <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">map</span>[<span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>]<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">struct</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         Type        <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>   <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;json:\\&quot;type\\&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         Description <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>   <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;json:\\&quot;description\\&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         Enum        []<span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;json:\\&quot;enum,omitempty\\&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        } <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;json:\\&quot;properties\\&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">       }{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        Type:     <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;object&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        Required: []<span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>{<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;city&quot;</span>},</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        Properties: <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">map</span>[<span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>]<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">struct</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         Type        <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>   <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;json:\\&quot;type\\&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         Description <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>   <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;json:\\&quot;description\\&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         Enum        []<span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;json:\\&quot;enum,omitempty\\&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        }{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;city&quot;</span>: {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">          Type:        <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;string&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">26</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">          Description: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The city to get the weather for&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">27</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         },</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">28</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        },</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">29</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">       },</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">30</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      },</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">31</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">     }</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>外部サービスの呼び出しを実現</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">processToolCall := <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(cr api.Chat.Response)</span></span> (<span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>, <span class=\"hljs-type\">error</span>) {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">   <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> _, v := <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">range</span> cr.Message.ToolCalls {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> v.Function.Name == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;getCurrentWeather&quot;</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> fmt.Sprintf(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;the weather of %v is 64 and sunny&quot;</span>, v.Function.Arguments[<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;city&quot;</span>]), <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">   }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>, errors.ErrUnsupported</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>chains を実現</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">uri, err := url.Parse(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;http://localhost:11434&quot;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">panic</span>(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">client := api.NewClient(uri, &amp;http.Client{})</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">messages := []api.Message{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">   Role:    <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;user&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">   Content: prompt,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  },</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">ctx := context.TODO()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">err := o.llm.Chat(ctx,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  &amp;api.ChatRequest{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">   Model:    <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;qwen2.5:32b-instruct&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">   Stream:   lo.ToPtr(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">   Messages: messages,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digit